This program has O(m + n) * log(m) complexity by time and O(n * m) by space.

Those nasty test cases where there can be multiple paths from one node to the *same* other node... 
Anyway, my solution ended up hitting a TLE, even though it was otherwise correct; I just should have used a binary search approach.
